Results.PublicRemarks: This is it!! A 2011 5th Wheel located presently at The Big Tent RV Park. This unit has A/C, Propane Furnace, Solar Panel with batteries & 12V convertor, LED bulbs in all fixtures and 3 bump outs. A built in flat screen tv that lowers into a cabinet, Corian counters, Hot water on Demand, a large fridge and a new range, large bedroom with Queen size and large bath. Also has a dehumidifier, vacuum, custom entry stairs and lots of storage and many extras. This park is situated on the edge of the beautiful Englishman River. This year-round park has the same low monthly rate all year with power, cable and garbage service included. Small pets are allowed with park approval and must be leashed when outdoors. There is also laundry, showers and an outdoor pool for the guests. The Park is within walking distance to downtown shopping and restaurants. Oceanside and Rathtrevor parks are also just a short walk away. Living here is an inexpensive way to enjoy all this beautiful area has to offer. (22146485)

Results.PublicRemarks: Excellent opportunity to obtain a 1/4 share in the Old House Hotel & Spa. This corner unit has stunning river and garden views at a great price. This unit is fully furnished, has a spacious living room, an electric fireplace, fully equipped kitchen, and is maintained immaculately by management. There is a king size bed and second TV in the bedroom as well as in suite laundry. Enjoy use of the luxurious hotel spa, pool and hot tub or take a walk on the river way trail system where minutes away you'll find access to kayak rental. This hotel is centrally located near all amenities including skiing and golf. This is a great opportunity for someone to have a recreational property without the hassle of taking care of it and at the same time receiving a positive income flow from the renting of the suite in the hotel rental pool.
